Rule: If workclass is "Self-Employed", then the likelihood of earning more than $50k increases.
If education is "Doctorate", "Prof-school", or "Masters", then the likelihood of earning more than $50k increases.
If marital_status is "Married", "Separated", or "Divorced", then the likelihood of earning more than $50k increases.
If age is significantly higher (e.g., 60 years), then the likelihood of earning more than $50k increases.
If hours_per_week is increased, then the likelihood of earning more than $50k increases.
